  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Available on bed and breakfast, there's plenty of choice in the hotel's 'Tata' restaurant. Enjoy fresh bread, cheeses, cold cuts, cereals, fruit as well as freshly brewed coffee and tea.</p>
<p>Enjoy free après snacks served daily from 4pm - 6pm.</p>
<p>If you choose to eat at the hotel for dinner, there is a bistro and a gourmet restaurant, 'Tata', which are both payable locally. Dining in the charming Lo Restò Tatà, you can enjoy tasty evening meals which are inspired by the Val d'Ayas, with organic, seasonal and local products used throughout the menu. Alternatively, you can head to Lo Bistrot, located 3 minutes from the hotel, and enjoy delicious meals during lunch and dinner. If you are staying over Christmas or New Year, we highly recommend booking the restaurant directly with the hotel well in advance.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
