  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Au Charmant Petit Lac is the newest addition to Champoluc's hotel scene. It's a stunningly modern mountain lodge with cosy fireplaces, comfy rooms and a great spa with an impossible-to-resist indoor pool. The breakfast is great too and don't forget a nightcap in front of the open fire in the lobby.</p>]]></listingDescription>
